---
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
import { Target, Zap, Heart } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="About - Henzi's Services LLC">
	<section class="py-20 md:py-32">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center space-y-4 mb-16">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold">
						About{" "}
						<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 dark:from-purple-400 dark:to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
							Henzi's Services
						</span>
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
						We build AI-powered tools for real people — not just tech teams
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Founder Section -->
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 mb-16 p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-card">
					<img
						src="/Henzi.png"
						alt="Joe Henzi"
						class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full object-cover object-top shrink-0 shadow-lg"
					/>
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Joe Henzi</h2>
						<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">
							Founder, Henzi's Services LLC &bull;
							<a href="https://henzi.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Henzi.org</a>
							&bull; Henzi Foundation
						</p>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
							Joe is a Salesforce professional with over 10 years of experience building software in the enterprise. He's spent his career solving real business problems with technology — and was among the first 0.1% of ChatGPT users when AI went mainstream, recognizing immediately what it could mean for the tools people use every day.
						</p>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
							That excitement led directly to
							<a href="https://mlswriter.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">MLS Writer</a>,
							<a href="https://pacalaca.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Pacalaca</a>,
							and <a href="https://vote.henzi.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">VOTE</a> — three tools built on a simple belief: make something genuinely useful, keep it accessible, and get out of the user's way.
						</p>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground">
							Through <a href="https://henzi.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Henzi.org</a> and the Henzi Foundation, Joe has extended that same mission — creating software and initiatives that put real people first.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Story Section -->
				<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mx-auto mb-16">
					<h2>Our Story</h2>
					<p>
						Henzi's Services LLC was founded with a straightforward belief: the best software solves a real problem for a real person.
						Too much technology is built for people who already know how to use technology. We build for everyone else.
					</p>
					<p>
						Our first product, MLS Writer, came from watching real estate agents spend hours writing listing copy — tedious,
						repetitive work that an AI can do in seconds while keeping it Fair Housing compliant. Pacalaca came from watching
						people avoid investing entirely because every tool assumed they already understood it. And VOTE came from watching
						engineering teams burn cycles in prioritization debates that math should settle in minutes.
					</p>
					<p>
						We distribute all three products under Henzi's Services LLC. As we grow, we'll keep applying the same principle:
						find a workflow that's harder than it needs to be, and fix it.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Mission & Goals -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
					<div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card">
						<div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 mb-4">
							<Target class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Mission</h3>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground">
							Provide material support for the development of software built for humans — tools that reduce friction and create real value for real people.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card">
						<div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 mb-4">
							<Zap class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Approach</h3>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground">
							Ship focused tools that do one thing well. No bloat, no steep learning curves — just tools that work. Excess income funds the Henzi Foundation.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card">
						<div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-rose-500 mb-4">
							<Heart class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Values</h3>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground">
							Build for the user, not the pitch deck. Accessible by design. Honest about what our products do and don't do.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Products -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
					<a href="https://mlswriter.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">MLS Writer →</h3>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
							AI-generated MLS listings, social media posts, and blog content — all Fair Housing compliant — in seconds.
						</p>
					</a>
					<a href="https://pacalaca.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Pacalaca →</h3>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
							Investing for humans. A platform built to make investing understandable and accessible to everyday people.
						</p>
					</a>
					<a href="https://vote.henzi.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">VOTE →</h3>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
							WSJF-powered prioritization for engineering teams. Decide what to do next — without overthinking.
						</p>
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Henzi Foundation Free Projects -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<div class="text-center mb-10">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Gifts from the Henzi Foundation</h2>
						<p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
							Not every project needs a price tag. These are free experiments and art projects — given away because building them was worthwhile in itself.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
						<a href="https://henzi.org/news-pulse-live-art-application.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500 to-indigo-500 shrink-0">
									<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
										<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
										<circle cx="5" cy="8" r="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.6" />
										<circle cx="19" cy="6" r="2.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5" />
										<circle cx="7" cy="17" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4" />
										<circle cx="18" cy="17" r="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7" />
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1 text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 group-hover:underline">Pulsefield →</h3>
									<p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
										A real-time visualization that transforms global headlines into a living work of digital art. News topics cluster as pulsing 3D orbs — color-coded by sentiment, sized by volume, alive with the moment.
									</p>
									<p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-2">pulse.henzi.org</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</a>
						<a href="https://henzi.org/robot-diary.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-card hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-500 shrink-0">
									<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
										<rect x="7" y="3" width="10" height="8" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" />
										<circle cx="10" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" />
										<circle cx="14" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" />
										<path d="M10 9h4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
										<path d="M12 11v2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
										<rect x="5" y="13" width="14" height="7" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" />
										<path d="M8 17h8M8 15.5h5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6" />
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 group-hover:underline">The Personal Diary of B3N-T5-MNT →</h3>
									<p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
										An automated art project: a maintenance robot in New Orleans observes the world through a window and records its thoughts. Each entry weaves in real-time weather, news, moon phases, and the robot's own accumulated memory.
									</p>
									<p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-2">robot.henzi.org</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Henzi Foundation & The Frankie Fund -->
				<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 dark:from-purple-950/30 dark:to-pink-950/30 mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">The Henzi Foundation &amp; The Frankie Fund</h2>
					<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 max-w-2xl">
						Henzi's Services LLC exists in part to generate the resources needed to sustain and expand the Henzi Foundation's work.
						Excess income from our products is dedicated to the Foundation — specifically the <strong>Frankie Fund</strong>, our primary charitable vehicle.
					</p>
					<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 max-w-2xl">
						As we grow, our hope is to expand into areas that matter most to us: <strong>Child Safety</strong> and the <strong>Environment</strong> — reduce, reuse, recycle, save the planet, and help defer global warming. The work we do building useful software today is the foundation for the impact we want to have tomorrow.
					</p>
					<a href="https://henzi.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-6 rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
						Visit Henzi.org
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
